      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a fantastic car for me. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved\u2014it runs beautifully and is ready to hit the road with a new owner today! It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a reliable, great-looking vehicle without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve taken care of the maintenance, so you can just hop in and go. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
