    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E92 M3 powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, featuring individual throttle bodies and a factory 8,400 RPM redline. This unit is mechanically sound, having undergone preventative rod bearing and throttle actuator service to ensure valvetrain and induction longevity. The chassis features M-specific kinematics and an M Variable Differential Lock for superior power delivery through corners. While the exterior shows minor stone chips and patina consistent with enthusiast use, the 6-speed manual gearbox and hydraulic steering rack offer an analog experience lost in modern iterations. A robust example of the last naturally aspirated M-car.",
